<p><strong>SCP-1692：</strong>你知道我不能自助</p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/andarielhalo" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1750255); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1750255&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600571125" alt="AndarielHalo" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1750255)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/andarielhalo" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1750255); return false;">AndarielHalo</a></span></p>
<p>来尝更多我的SCP。<a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/andariel-halo-file" target="_blank">全部吃掉。</a></p>
